attributes.title: Toks Olagundoye
attributes.twitter: https://twitter.com/toksolagundoye'''Toks Olagundoye''' (born September 16, 1975) is a Nigerian actress. She is best known for her role as Jackie Joyner-Kersee in the ABC TV sitcom ''The Neighbours''. She has also appeared in television series such as ''Law & Order'', ''Ugly Betty'', ''CSI: NY'', ''NCIS'' and ''Prime Suspect''.In ''Game of Thrones: A Telltale Games Series'', she voices Beskha.==Credits==Telltale Game Series Credits
